{"tid":2335931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同kelly一齊過嘅Christmas month","createTime":"2020-12-22T08:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T16:54:04.000Z","uid":307910,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f37e71157920e1b426b7c79b60940af191b428f7","tid":2335931,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:41:35.000Z","msg":"記得佢成日都話我著衫好柒，所以有一日就話帶我去買衫，咁我記得就行咗入去一間gu<br />\n「嘩！你睇下幾抵，80蚊就有一件衫」<br />\n「係喎。」<br />\n「你睇下呢條裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「條裙咁短，依家又咁凍。」<br />\n「乜你咁撚煩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「唔係呀你著都幾靚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n然之後就見到賣頸巾嘅嗰個攤位，我記得之前真係返緊學嘅時候，有一日又係冬天，得唔知9度定10度，我唔知唔夠瞓定係咩，就好似有少少感冒定唔知點，著住6件濕鳩校服嬲，凍撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢之後就行埋嚟，問我係唔係好凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我話ok啦，佢就係頸上面，除咗佢條紅色底綠色格仔嘅闊頸巾，然之後當著全世界面前，幫我戴起<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大佬呀，有個咁嘅女仔幫你戴頸巾，點可能唔鐘意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（條頸巾仲要好撚香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「你做咩眼定定望住堆頸巾？你睇到有啱嘅款？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「無，諗返起一啲以前嘅嘢咋嘛」<br />\n「諗起以前嘅嘢啫」<br />\n「前度?」<br />\n「你。」<br />\n<br />\n之後大家都無出聲，咩都無買就行出咗gu<br />\n<br />\n之後我哋就行咗去一間百貨公司，睇下啲風扇呀，廚具呀之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，總之就每樣嘢都試下睇下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，嗰時佢又開始講佢啲情史<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n「我之前同佢拍過兩次拖架，復合嗰一日仲要係同一齊嗰日都係同一日」<br />\n呢個就係之前佢第一次攬我嗰次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其實可能嗰時我大膽啲，佢已經唔會同呢個男仔復合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我就係度諗點解我咁細膽，其實好多時自己都係唔夠膽先至咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行行下我哋就見到塊連身鏡：<br />\n「妖，你唔好企係我後面啦，成隻兵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「咁我係你隻兵啊嘛(講笑咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)」<br />\n「企我右手邊！」<br />\n「左手邊唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「以前xxx都係企我右手邊」<br />\n（即刻行前企去佢右手邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n佢叫我企佢前度（唔係第一個）平時企開個位，咁樣講係咪暗示我可以做佢男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，定係我只係一件代替佢男朋友嘅汰除品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過有得做是啤我都受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁嗰時其實食完嘢，我哋都另外行咗兩，三個鐘。都成十點十一點，我就陪佢等巴士番屋企，咁巴士站嗰時就無人，kelly對我嘅語氣就開始有啲唔同咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲開始問埋啲奇奇怪怪嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「其實你有冇同你前度扑過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「吓...好尷尬喎，點樣答你好呀...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「講你就講啦，係咪姐係冇呀?」<br />\n「er...點講好呢，廣義嚟講可以話係有，但係實際嚟講其實又唔太可以話有...」<br />\n「你噏乜春呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「XXXXXXXXXXXX」<br />\n「屌姐係冇啦，青頭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n「<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n（我梗係知佢唔係，但無理由咁樣駁返佢架嘛，所以就忍住啖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n「好啦，我架巴士到啦，byebye」<br />\n「（扮唔care咁樣答佢）再約。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好甜，同一個無共同經歷嘅人，真係搵唔返呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過我要學習唔好be used to 呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人若變！快啲搵過第二個女仔，建立更加多嘅經歷，要有滿滿開心嘅回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實仲諗到好多野想出想講，不過p牌真心On9<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n如從前沒有毅力去表白亦便沒有今天這個我<br />\n覺得不開口講最愛 越愛得多"},{"pid":"1b8e5f1ce2372a3fd49b32bc4a0565b659651ebd","tid":2335931,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"有kelly post出無人講?"},{"pid":"5a776fc7a48667eaece089d5c0b42a2a98e727cd","tid":2335931,"uid":294925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885c29e90201ad0ff395fd21a52ee74ca988253f","tid":2335931,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.karousell.com/media/photos/products/2020/10/3/_japan_red_scarf_1601704566_b76440af_progressive.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.karousell.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fproducts%2F2020%2F10%2F3%2F_japan_red_scarf_1601704566_b76440af_progressive.jpg&h=1b9ef9bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰條頸巾嘅款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff59908d964b630621cede712f78312d4c54400","tid":2335931,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"885c29e90201ad0ff395fd21a52ee74ca988253f","tid":2335931,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.karousell.com/media/photos/products/2020/10/3/_japan_red_scarf_1601704566_b76440af_progressive.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.karousell.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fproducts%2F2020%2F10%2F3%2F_japan_red_scarf_1601704566_b76440af_progressive.jpg&h=1b9ef9bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰條頸巾嘅款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人知邊度有得賣呢種pattern嘅頸巾，想自己買嚟幫自己攬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577af5e100325718f5386a180226786e56b7b262","tid":2335931,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5a776fc7a48667eaece089d5c0b42a2a98e727cd","tid":2335931,"uid":294925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c758a7f0adf8763a915124065278536996b2b291","tid":2335931,"uid":142017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69516d940c5fc8e462d8ac3075c0e73cc5264712","tid":2335931,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c758a7f0adf8763a915124065278536996b2b291","tid":2335931,"uid":142017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T08:48:20.000Z","msg":"笑咩笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062a650531471e257bde570b6466b9b15b7d37ae","tid":2